facet .

tran_label <- function(string) {
  for(i in 1:length(string)) {
    temp <- df_high |> 
    filter( == string[i]) |>
    summarise(n = n()) |> pull()
    string[i] <- paste0(string[i], '(n=', temp, ')')
  }
  string
}

df_high |> 
  filter( < 3) |> 
  ggplot(aes(x = , y = )) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  geom_hline(aes(yintercept = 1), col = 'red') +
  facet_wrap(~, labeller = labeller( = tran_label)) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle= 90))
